Advanced Formulas and Functions
How to write formula in Excel?
1. Select the cell
2.Enter equals sign so excel knows a formula being entered
3.Using the example of the four times table
       > In cell E3 type : =A3*c3
       > Press enter
4.Select E3 and drag bottom right cornerdown to E12
5. The formula has been applied to all thse cells

Functions covered:
> SUM
> AVERAGE
> MAX
> MIN
> XLOOKUP
> SUMPRODUCT
> OFFSET
> QUERY
